{"word":"G5545 - χρῖσμα - chrîsma - khris'-mah - Anointing","slug":"G5545","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρῖσμα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chrîsma"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khris'-mah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Anointing"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C7;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BC;&#x03B1; - chrisma</b> - <i>khris'-mah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5548\">G5548</a>; an <i>unguent</i> or <i>smearing</i>, that is, (figuratively) the special <i>endowment</i> (&ldquo;chrism&rdquo;) of the Holy Spirit: - anointing, unction."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G500\">G500</a>, <a href=\"#/G5546\">G5546</a>, <a href=\"#/G5547\">G5547</a>, <a href=\"#/G5548\">G5548</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580\">G5580</a>"}]}